<h2>Common topics</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Sign in</strong> — Use Sign in with Apple. Bundles, sharing, and review need an account; Mushaf reading works without one.</li>
  <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Sharing a bundle</strong> — Create a bundle, add pages from the Mushaf, then share it with another signed-in user.</li>
  <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Review sessions</strong> — Listener follows pages and can mark mistakes; review marks appear in Feedback after the session.</li>
  <li><strong style="color: var(--text);">Bugs &amp; ideas</strong> — Use Send Feedback in the app drawer, or email us with your device model and iOS version.</li>
</ul>

<h2>App Store</h2>
